{"tid":455991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現屋企人偷用我支牙刷","createTime":"2017-11-02T14:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T15:47:00.000Z","uid":105480,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e679bffcbc58bf383a725997bd3e9888f2adb4","tid":455991,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"前晚入廁所諗住刷牙，見到我啊嫲支牙刷放左落我水杯，我枝牙刷就飛左出來<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/223849_0d66715d33fdef30de798ae4693dda4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F223849_0d66715d33fdef30de798ae4693dda4b.jpg&h=7f7b0fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左確認班廢老係咪真係攞我支牙刷用，我將支牙刷打直放。 示意圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/224201_e4038dda09b41b4e0f064f3b9ac1c2dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F224201_e4038dda09b41b4e0f064f3b9ac1c2dc.jpg&h=4ce4373c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚我番到屋企入廁所睇我支牙刷倒轉左擺，代表佢地用過我支牙刷。示意圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/224319_ee6f0c8c9ef913ecdd80c55c9b271399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F224319_ee6f0c8c9ef913ecdd80c55c9b271399.jpg&h=a0418cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n痴線 真係接受唔到屋企人用我支牙刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同屋企人共用牙刷真係好嘔心     <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一家人有咩咁出奇 係你自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d44b595d87bef7c75011935ec3aa00b2ba1676","tid":455991,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:50:58.000Z","msg":"阿嫲想錫你但又唔好意思，終於佢諗到依個咁間接嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b0ea57d2d904c076ea2076935bce53ba9fc43c","tid":455991,"